    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Torbj\u00f6rn places his Turret to lock down a chokepoint or flank route, alternating between Rivet Gun poke at range and close-range Forge Hammer swings when enemies get too close.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>The turret is a stationary, fragile investment that any dive hero can destroy in a couple of hits, and Torbj\u00f6rn himself has no mobility tool to escape once he's found.</p>"
